data.title: Carlsbad Groups and Parties
data.meta_description: Looking to book a birthday party, company event, or other special occasion at K1 Speed Carlsbad? Explore our pricing today by visiting this page.
data.text:
Your Place in Carlsbad for Birthday Parties, Corporate Events, Bachelor Parties, & More

No matter the reason, we can create an event for you in Carlsbad, CA that your guests will never forget. Whether you’re hosting a company party, celebrating a kid’s birthday party, throwing a client appreciation event or just looking for a unique outing with friends, K1 Speed is the perfect destination for a thrilling event with speed. All of our events offer reserved times so you won’t have to wait, private racing for your group, and a professional-style racing format that is exclusive to our group event packages!

To speak with an Event Specialist please call 1-855-517-7333.
